Functions
ut length
ut length(
UtMatcher matcher 
)

Passes the Length() of the actual value to the inner matcher.

Factory function for UtSizeMatcher.

Arguments
matcher
UtMatcher

any object

Examples
ut assert that( Expr( {1,2,3} ), ut length( 3 ) );
ut assert that( Expr( "str" || "ing" ), ut length( 6 ) );
